<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-lasChaquirasDeMai" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Part 1</p>
<ol>
      <li>C, because we can see the 104 beads she had, that she has 124 altogether, and the packs that she bought, but not how many are in each pack.</li>
      <li>A, because we can see how much she has all together and the 2 packs of 10, but not how much she had before.</li>
      <li>B, because we can see she started with 104 and the two packs as the two parts with 10, but you don’t know how many she has altogether.</li>
    </ol>
<p>Part 2</p>
<ol>
      <li>Situation 3</li>
      <li>Situation 1</li>
      <li>Situation 2</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


